---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="About - Broderick">
    <main class="container">
        <header class="hero">
            <h1>Hi!</h1>
            <p class="subtitle">Polymath, Engineer, Athlete</p>
        </header>

        <section class="about-content">
            <div class="about-main">
                <p>I love learning things, I would consider myself an extremely curious individual. When someone asks a question and 
                    I dont know the answer, I instantly have an urge to find out. I have spent hours reading Wikipedia articles on random topics only to 
                    have even more questions afterwards. This curiosity has given me the ability to genuinley find interest in anything, 
                    and I would definitely say that that is my biggest superpower. At times it is also a curse, as I can never seem to find enough time
                    to fit everything in. Thats why I started <a href="/experiments">Experiments</a></p>

                <p>
                </p>

                <p>I chose engineer because I believe at heart I am a problem solver. Whether it be something breaking and me quickly hacking a solution
                    or being on a walk and thinking of solutions to problems my friends have. I love creating things that have an impact. You can find my work on the <a href="/projects">Projects</a> page
                </p>

                <p>I believe sports have completely shaped how I think. You have to be able to visualize yourself from a different perspective, and visualize others perspectives. 
                    You have to be able to get back up, and keep going, even when you feel rock bottom. You keep trying, over and over again. Right when you're about to give up, you keep going, and you hit success. 
                    
                </p>
            </div>

            <aside class="about-sidebar">
                <ul class="socials-list">
                    <li><a href="mailto:me@brody.gg"><strong>Email</strong> me@brody.gg</a></li>
                    <li><a href="https://x.com/home" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer"><strong>Twitter</strong> @Brodylame</a></li>
                    <li><a href="https://github.com/M3kko" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer"><strong>GitHub</strong> @M3kko</a></li>
                    <li><a href="https://www.instagram.com/brody_lane/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer"><strong>Instagram</strong> @brody_lane</a></li>
                    <li><a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/broderickc/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer"><strong>LinkedIn</strong> @Broderickc</a></li>
                </ul>
            </aside>

        </section>
    </main>
</Layout>

<style>
    .about-content {
        position: relative;
        margin-top: 3rem;
    }

    .about-main {
        max-width: 66.666%;
    }

    .about-main p {
        font-size: 1.125rem;
        line-height: 1.8;
        margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    }

    .about-main a {
        color: var(--accent);
        text-decoration: none;
        font-weight: 500;
    }

    .about-main a:hover {
        text-decoration: underline;
    }

    .about-sidebar {
        position: absolute;
        top: 0;
        left: calc(66.666% + 1.333rem);
        width: auto;
    }

    .socials-list {
        list-style: none;
        padding: 0;
        margin: 0;
    }

    .socials-list li {
        margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
        font-size: 1.25rem;
        line-height: 1.6;
    }

    .socials-list a {
        color: var(--text);
        text-decoration: none;
        font-weight: 600;
        display: flex;
        gap: 0.5rem;
        white-space: nowrap;
        transition: all 0.2s ease;
        padding: 0.25rem 0.5rem;
        margin: -0.25rem -0.5rem;
        border-radius: 4px;
    }

    .socials-list a:hover {
        background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05);
        cursor: pointer;
        box-shadow: 0 1px 0 0 var(--text);
    }

    @media (max-widdth: 768px) {
        .about-content {
            grid-template-columns: 1fr;
        }

        .about-sidebar {
            position: static;
            margin-top: 2rem;
        }



    }

</style>
